      "raw_text": "G.. r. Schlauch, candidate for the\nrepublican nomination for county\nsuperintendent of schools, was in\nthe city today. Mr.. Schlauch is\nprincipal of the Latah schools, and\nis endorsed by the County Princi-\npals association for the office.\n\n\nThe County Principals associa-\nton believes that for the post of\ncounty superintendent of schools a\nman from the rural schools should\nbe selected, as the duties Of the\noffice are entirely with the district\nschools. 1t is understood that Pro-\nfessor Yeager Of the city schools\nhas announced his intention OF\nmaking the race. and 1t Is against"
